00:42:26.260 --> 00:42:31.540
[Amit Varma]: You know, T20 cricket changed so much, not just in terms of commerce in the sense that

00:42:31.540 --> 00:42:36.860
[Amit Varma]: it brought a new viewership to the game, and it also allowed a much wider pool of people

00:42:36.860 --> 00:42:39.380
[Amit Varma]: to make a living than was otherwise happening.

